{DIALOGUE}: Yeah...my mother made it from a kit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Jan sees an almost imperceptible mother pang in Chris, but he pushes it away quickly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHRIS (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: I'm gonna sleep out here by the fire.
{DIALOGUE}: I want to read a little bit.
