{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CHAPTER 2: ADOLESCENCE
{META_DATA}: DISSOLVE TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 48 EXT. CASCADE RANGE - DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: MUSIC OVER: Joe Henry's King's Highway
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A SERIES OF SHOTS:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 1.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chris hitchhiking through the Sage Brush Uplands
