{DIALOGUE}: These guys come off the Hudderite colony looking for work.
{DIALOGUE}: I always got work for people.
{DIALOGUE}: Then that guy -
{META_DATA}: (MORE)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 42A.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: WAYNE (CONT'D)
