{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 12.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Tracy at a high school dance, slow-dancing with her young date.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 13.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Looking through the windshield of another semi.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A bear lopes across the two-lane road before us.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We PAN and ZOOM with it into the tundra beside the road.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: HANDHELD, WALKING, we pass Mile 0 of the Alaska highway: The sign: Fairbanks 1523 miles.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 14.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A waterfall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 15.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Intercut hand and thumb hitching - a sense that rides are few and far between.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 16.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A misting mountain peak.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 17.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Beavers in streams.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 18.
