{META_DATA}: (Through Johnson's Crossing, Whitehorse, and Beaver Creek.)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 22.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: From a passenger car window, a series of road signs reading: Closed for winter.
{META_DATA}: MUSIC FADE OUT
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 121.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 211 INT. MCCANDLESS HOME, ANNANDALE - DAY
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CARINE (V.O.)
{DIALOGUE}: About a month short of the second anniversary of Chris' disappearance, I had gotten engaged to my boyfriend Jerry Ray and was moving in with him...
