{CHARACTER_NAME}: CARINE (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: Who wrote that?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHRIS
{DIALOGUE}: Well, it could've been either one of us.
{DIALOGUE}: Couldn't it?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: We see pictures of Chris on the night-stand of Walt and Billie's bedroom
